Tri-Anglers Lunchtime Fishing

																																													May 8, 2024 - Oct 2, 2024																										
								Join us for Tri-Anglers, a free fishing program that has been running for over 22 years in downtown Pittsburgh! We catch and release a variety species of fish along the Allegheny River – bass, carp, catfish, freshwater drum, and more! No prior fishing experience needed and great activity for all ages.								READ MORE






